settings.heading: Dip Powder
settings.text:
Our Dip Powders are manufactured with the most effective formula that makes your nails feel natural without any damage to the nail beds.

The dip powder is a healthier alternative to acrylic with the same durability.

Lasts up to 3 weeks on natural nails. Fast and easy application process!

Soak off process is quick and easy, leaving your nails healthy without any damage.

settings.custom_liquid: WE ARE ALL ABOUT A HEALTHIER ALTERNATIVE

settings.heading: Gel Polish
settings.text:
Gel Polish Our 3 Step Soak Off Gel is formulated with utmost precision towards ensuring quality. Giving you the 14 FREE toxic ingredients. The gel polish offers long-lasting wear and an irresistible shine through a quick and easy application process.

The Gel Polish lasts up to 2 weeks at minimum, without any lifting or chipping and comes in a variety of rich and dreamy colours.

Soak off process is quick and easy leaving your nails healthy without any damage.

settings.custom_liquid: NO MORE NAIL DAMAGE

settings.heading: Hybrid Gel
settings.text:
Hybrid GelThe Hybrid Gel is a hybrid between an acrylic and a hard gel. Giving you the best of both in one!

This enhancement is easy to apply by giving you infinite application time and no chasing.

This product is suitable for all clients and can be used for sculpting and overlays.

Soak off process is quick and easy leaving your nails healthy without any damage.
